= 1967, alone.

{!<button onclick="killfunction();">!}aa{!</button>!}

{!
<div class="typewriter dialogue1" id="clicktest">!}


{!<table>

            
            </table>!}

Life ended this day, the life that you knew, everything that you had known was shattered by six bullets, two and four in your two parents.

Blood spilled on the pavement, the wind ripping away the last warmth you felt, you felt nothing else in this place to move forward.

As you moved home, your life had been irrevocably derailed, you needed to find one way out.

{!</div>!}

- @promises: Debug skip to promises.
- @1967_justice: You needed to bring those that would do such a thing to justice.
- @1967_vengeance: You swore that you will have vengeance for what happened.
- @1967_never: You saw that nothing like this should ever happen to anyone.


